query:
INSERT INTO users (id, email, display_name)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
        ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
        SET email = EXCLUDED.email,
            display_name = EXCLUDED.display_name,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING
            id           AS "id!",
            email        AS "email!",
            display_name AS "display_name!",
            created_at   AS "created_at!",
            updated_at   AS "updated_at!"
